EXTRACTED VALUE: I positively loved this book (as I did the first one). Couldn't put it down........I can hardly wait for the next one to come out.
This is the best read on heaven - academically strong, but written in a winsome way, so we put our affection above.
Good story. Although Terrorism is not my thing, the book was well written, kept my interest to the end.
I didn't like the part about the stink bugs because I don't like bugs. I did like the part where Rachael got a kitten.
